name: Prosecutor Princess
overview: Ma Hye Ri is a woman with an excellent memory and ability to focus, which allowed her to pass the bar exam with ease. Despite her talents, she is more interested in being fashionable and dislikes hard work, so she is far from being an ideal prosecutor and has doubts about her suitability for her job. Through her conflicts with senior colleagues and struggles with difficult cases, however, Hye Ri gradually matures into a brilliant prosecutor with a sense of duty and justice.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Law school grad Ma Hye Ri ditches her graduation ceremony, with the help of her mother, to hit the slopes for a weekend of fun and fashion. However, her plans hit a speed bump suddenly when trouble strikes.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Hye Ri runs into familiar faces on her first day at work. Her carefree lifestyle ruffles some feathers.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Hye Ri finds herself enveloped in a scandal and must swallow her pride. To prove herself to her co-workers she takes on an illegal gambling case with Seo In Woo's help.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Hye Ri's failed investigation results in Prosecutors Yoon coming to her aid. In Woo continues to help Hye Ri as his feelings grow.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: In Woo gives Hye Ri a wake up call as she tries to run away from her responsibilities once more.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: As Hye Ri and In Woo work as opposing attorneys on the same case, a photo from her past comes back to haunt her. Hye Ri fakes a car accident to get her parents' permission to move out of the house.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: Hye Ri moves into Prosecutor Yoon's neighborhood with hopes of going on a picnic date with him, but gets more than she bargained for.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Jealous of Hye Ri and Prosecutor Yoon, In Woo tries to come between them. However, Prosecutor Yoon warns Hye Ri to be suspicious of In Woo.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: Hye Ri becomes suspicious of In Woo's attentions and starts to wonder about his true intentions. Meanwhile, strange events begin happening in Hye Ri's apartment.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Hye Ri solves a murder case through persistent effort. In Woo's discovery about Hye Ri forces him to make a difficult decision.

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: Hye Ri's current case brings her to a startling revelation about her father.

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview: Prosecutor Yoon lends an ear to Hye Ri, who is hurt and confused when In Woo leaves without notice.

episodes.name: Episode 13
episodes.overview: When In Yoo's true identity and intentions are revealed, Hye Ri is devastated.

episodes.name: Episode 14
episodes.overview: Hye Ri and In Woo's relationship is strengthened as they revisit their shared past. Hye Ri meets with Mr. Shin, who has the key to incriminating her own father.

episodes.name: Episode 15
episodes.overview: Hye Ri confronts her father and finally learns the truth about his business dealings. In Woo volunteers to be the lawyer for Mr. Ma's case.

episodes.name: Episode 16
episodes.overview: Prosecutor Yoon, Hye Ri and In Woo fight the case against her father, and Mr. Ma formally apologizes to In Woo for the first time.
